<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Walter </PERSON> <PERSON> R. </PERSON> <PERSON> Mears </PERSON>, vice president and columnist for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>, has reported on <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> and national politics for more than 25 years. End Adv PM Thurs Aug.
