 Elsewhere in television: STORYBOOK HOST _ <PERSON> Danny </PERSON> <PERSON> Glover </PERSON> will be the host of the third season of <PERSON> Showtime </PERSON>'s `` Storybook Classics,'' which premieres Tuesday, Sept. 12. The opening show is `` Thumbelina,'' narrated by <PERSON> Kelly </PERSON> <PERSON> McGillis </PERSON>, a former host. <PERSON> Glenn </PERSON> <PERSON> Close </PERSON> is another former host.
