 <PERSON> Virgil </PERSON> <PERSON> C. </PERSON> <PERSON> Dechant </PERSON>, supreme knight of the Knights of <LOCATION> Columbus </LOCATION>, urges <ORGANIZATION> Catholic </ORGANIZATION> lay people to be more supportive of their bishops. In the 1.5-million-member <ORGANIZATION> Catholic </ORGANIZATION> organization's monthly magazine, <ORGANIZATION> Columbia </ORGANIZATION>, <PERSON> Dechant </PERSON> writes that skepticism and unbelief are `` especially acute'' and that bishops `` need our support and collaboration. `` In this age of widespread unbelief, evangelization calls for the best efforts of us all.''
