 In an history-making ecumenical step, the recent general assembly of the <ORGANIZATION> Christian </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Church </ORGANIZATION> -LRB- Disciples of Christ -RRB- elected a Roman Catholic priest, Monsignor <PERSON> Philip </PERSON> <PERSON> Morris </PERSON>, as a member of the 1.1-million-member denomination's governing board.
