<FIRST>u f BC-BoardofTrade Close   08-30 0207</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Board of Trade, Close,0215</SECOND>
<HEAD>Wheat Futures Dip; Corn, Soybeans Mixed</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
